FBIS4-38922 "drsov107_p_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Senior Prosecutor Escapes Assassination Attempt Senior Prosecutor Escapes Assassination Attempt LD0206080994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0742 GMT 2 Jun 94 LD0206080994 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Tigran Liloyan] [Text] Yerevan June 2 TASS -- An attempt was staged early on Thursday on the life of Vladimir Grigoryan, the head of the investigation department of the Armenian prosecutor's office. A gunman opened submachine gun fire at him when he came out of his home heading for office. Grigoryan was not wounded; however, the driver of his car got a bullet wound. The gunman escaped and the site of the attack has been barricaded by police. No official statements on the incident have been made yet.
